OL,3,CJudge rules Donaldson trail to open
OL,4,Cnext week
OL,6,FA judge has ruled the trial of Sir
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson for alleged
OL,8,Fhistorical child sex offences and a
OL,9,Ftrial of facts for his wife will be
OL,10,Fheld at the same time next week.
OL,12,FThe judge had previously heard legal
OL,13,Fsubmissions on whether that trial of
OL,14,Fthe facts should run alongside the
OL,15,Ftrial of Jeffrey Donaldson or as
OL,16,Fseparate proceedings at a different
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,FThe former DUP leader is charged with
OL,20,Fand denies 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
