PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779700299
OL,3,CJudge rules Donaldson trail to open
OL,4,Cnext week
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,9,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008,
OL,10,Finvolving two alleged victims.
OL,12,FEleanor Donaldson, 60, from Dromore,
OL,13,Fhas denied charges of aiding and
OL,14,Fabetting.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, the trial judge ruled
OL,17,Fshe was unfit to stand trail and would
OL,18,Finstead face a trial of facts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
