FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779700299
OL,3,CJudge rules Donaldson trail to open
OL,4,Cnext week
OL,6,FIt is a provision under the 1986
OL,7,FMental Health Order allowing for the
OL,8,Fevidence to be put before a jury. The
OL,9,Faccused does not take part in the
OL,10,Fproceedings and can not be found
OL,11,Fguilty. Instead, the jury is asked to
OL,12,Fdetermine if they committed the
OL,13,Foffence. And although they can not be
OL,14,Fconvicted, they can be acquitted.
OL,16,FThe trial will open on Tuesday with
OL,17,Fjury selection with the opening
OL,18,Fstatements on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
