PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779700299
OL,3,CJudge rules Donaldson trail to open
OL,4,Cnext week
OL,6,FDelivering his ruling, the judge said:
OL,7,F"The interests of justice require that
OL,8,Fthis case be progressed in a manner
OL,9,Fthat is fair to all parties, but also
OL,10,Fas expediously as such fairness
OL,11,Fpermits.
OL,13,F"Accordingly I rule that the trial of
OL,14,FJeffrey Donaldson and the trial of the
OL,15,Ffacts of Eleanor Donaldson be held
OL,16,Fsimultaneously and the case will
OL,17,Fcommence on Tuesday next, the 26th of
OL,18,FMay."
OL,20,FNeither Jeffrey or Eleanor Donaldson
OL,21,Fwere present in court for the ruling.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
