OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779700299
OL,3,CJudge rules Donaldson trail to open
OL,4,Cnext week
OL,6,FThey were not required to attend.
OL,8,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,9,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,10,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,11,FMarch 2024.
OL,13,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,14,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,15,Fallegations emerged.
OL,17,FWeeks before his arrest, he had led
OL,18,Fthe DUP back into devolved government
OL,19,Fat Stormont after a two-year boycott
OL,20,Fof the powersharing institutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
